<template>
    <select class="select2-obj" style="width: 100%" ref="select2Obj">
        <option v-for="dept in options" :key="dept[keys[0]]" :value="dept[keys[0]]">{{dept.keys[1]}}</option>
    </select>
</template>

<script>
    import $ from "jquery";

    export default {
        name: "AppSelect2",
        props: ['options', 'keys'],
        mounted() {
            $(this.$refs.select2Obj).select2({
                width: 'resolve'
            });
        }
    }
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
